<h4><strong>CASS Certified&trade; for address correction</strong></h4>
<p>Standardize abbreviations and address formats to USPS&trade;  guidelines, correct the spelling of streets and 
cities and verify deliverability, includes DPV&reg;, LACSLink&reg; and SuiteLink&trade; processing. 
