<h4><strong>PAVE&trade; certified postal presortingv</strong></h4>
<p>Sort address lists for the lowest possible postal rates and generate all required USPS&trade;
documentation, reports and postage statements. The service includes support for First-Class Mai&reg; 
and Standard Mail&reg;.</p>
<p>The leading experts in enterprise grade software as a service &lpar;SaaS&rpar; for presort and 
