processing module. With powerful back-end Presort and CASS engines powered by SAP&reg;, real-time
processing is delivered on-demand, through the cloud.</p>
<p>Think you’ll be a frequent user? The FlexStreams USPS&trade; module has a purchasable annual 
subscription which can be added onto your solution for an additional fee. If you’ll only use the 
module occasionally, that’s okay as well. There’s also an as-needed, pay-as-you-go pricing plan for
